# Keep the build context small and force a clean install/build in the image.
.git
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dist-css
**/.vite
**/*.tsbuildinfo
scratch
tmp
*.log

# Both public images use `COPY . .`. Keep local operator/developer credentials
# out of the build context even when a nested tool has gitignored them (for
# example `.deepsec/.env.local`). These files must be injected at runtime.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.netrc
**/.git-credentials
**/.ssh
**/.aws
**/.config/gcloud
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
